About US

Let us tell you a little about ourselves and what we do...

RACE

A Computer Science and Engineering Association to connect with like-minded individuals, access cutting-edge resources, and engage in innovative projects shaping the future of technology. The Association is comprised of dedicated students and faculty members, collaboratively organizes a myriad of events, workshops, and initiatives aimed at fostering academic excellence, professional development, and community engagement within the realm of computer science and engineering.
